ps://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24247004/google -c2pa-verify-ai- generated-images-content&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24247004/google-c2pa-verify-ai-generated-images-content" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24247004/google-c2pa-verify-ai- generated-images-content</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-17T08:03:31-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-17T08:03:31-04:00</updated><title> Instagram 正在将每个青少年放入一个更加私密和限制性的新帐户</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Instagram 中显示青少年帐户的图片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/KXe1KTvn6YcLjU9h1iSovxr0DGc=/0x0:5760x3840/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/73590950/teen_account_instagram.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图像：元&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Y2NNIz&quot;>;从今天开始，Instagram 将开始&lt;a href=&quot;https: //about.fb.com/news/2024/09/instagram-teen-accounts/&quot;>;将 18 岁以下的新用户和现有用户&lt;/a>;放入“青少年账户”——此举将影响数十数百万青少年与该平台互动。新的帐户类型会自动对年轻用户应用一组保护，只有 16 岁及以上的用户才能放松其中一些设置。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;stjels&quot;>;对于初学者来说，所有未成年人的帐户Instagram 上的内容默认为私有（不仅仅是 16 岁以下的青少年），并且会附带 Instagram 针对年轻用户的一些现有限制，例如阻止 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1 /25/24050207/meta-instagram-messenger-messaging-restrictions-minors-teens-parental-settings&quot;>;陌生人直接向他们发送消息&lt;/a>;。但其他新功能也即将推出，包括从晚上 10 点到早上 7 点静音通知的睡眠模式。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tHoOyP&quot;>;“这确实标准化了很多......&lt;/p>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24246423/instagram-teen-account-private-restrictive&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24246423/instagram-teen-account-private-restrictive" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24246423/instagram-teen-account-private-restrictive</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-17T08:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-17T08:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Apple Watch Series 10 评测：超时尚的外观</title><content type="html">&lt;p>;Series 10 在更大的显示屏和更耐磨的设计上下了很大的赌注。就迭代更新而言，这是一个明智的选择。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24246464/apple-watch-series-10-review-smartwatch-wearables&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24246464/apple-watch-series-10-review-smartwatch-wearables" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24246464/apple-watch-series-10-review-smartwatch-wearables</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry></feed>